---
import ThemeInit from '../../components/tiles/ThemeInit.astro';
import ThemeToggle from '../../components/tiles/ThemeToggle.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Style tiles — takispap.com Phase 1</title>
		<ThemeInit />
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<img src="/logo.svg" alt="tp mark" width="40" height="40" />
			<ThemeToggle />
		</header>
		<main>
			<h1>Three directions. Pick, mix, or push back.</h1>
			<p>
				Phase 1 style tiles for takispap.com — same content, three temperaments. Each shows type, colour (both themes), spacing, components, motion and a 404 sample. Theme follows your system; the toggle overrides it. These pages are working artefacts: the winner becomes <code>design.md</code>, the losers get deleted.
			</p>
			<nav aria-label="Style tiles">
				<a href="/tiles/a" class="tile-card" style="view-transition-name: tile-a">
					<strong>A — Warm cinematic dark · WORKING DIRECTION (v2)</strong>
					<span>takis's pick, evolving: per-word scroll reveal, fluid full-width layout, inline SVG + Lucide icons, circular theme switch, focus halo.</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/tiles/b" class="tile-card" style="view-transition-name: tile-b">
					<strong>B — Editorial precision light</strong>
					<span>The henriheymans/karinasirqueira pole: warm paper, serif display, hairlines, zero cinema. Light-led.</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/tiles/c" class="tile-card" style="view-transition-name: tile-c">
					<strong>C — The hybrid</strong>
					<span>Calm light content, alive dark home/lab — plus the living accent: the site keeps Athens time.</span>
				</a>
			</nav>
			<p class="fonts-link"><a href="/tiles/fonts">Font specimens →</a> your eight faces, live — weight sliders, theme + accent picker.</p>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
	:root { color-scheme: light dark; }
	:root[data-theme='light'] { color-scheme: light; }
	:root[data-theme='dark'] { color-scheme: dark; }
	@view-transition { navigation: auto; }

	* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; }
	body {
		/* hex fallbacks first, OKLCH via light-dark() for capable browsers */
		background: #faf5ee;
		background: light-dark(oklch(97.2% 0.011 76.6), oklch(18.6% 0.008 48.3));
		color: #201913;
		color: light-dark(oklch(22% 0.016 62.5), oklch(94.1% 0.015 70.9));
		font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
		min-height: 100dvh;
		padding: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		max-width: 52rem;
		margin-inline: auto;
	}
	header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
	h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 1.2rem + 2.5vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
	main > p { max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
	nav { display: grid; gap: 1rem; }
	.tile-card {
		display: grid; gap: 0.35rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 6px;
		border: 1px solid;
		border-color: #dfd3c2;
		border-color: light-dark(oklch(87.2% 0.027 76.8), oklch(32.1% 0.018 60));
		color: inherit; text-decoration: none;
		transition: border-color 120ms ease, translate 120ms ease;
	}
	.tile-card:hover, .tile-card:focus-visible { border-color: currentColor; translate: 0 -2px; }
	.tile-card span { opacity: 0.75; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; }
	.fonts-link { margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
	.fonts-link a { color: inherit; }
	#theme-toggle {
		font: inherit; font-size: 0.85rem; cursor: pointer; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
		border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid currentColor; background: none; color: inherit;
	}
	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.tile-card { transition: none; }
	}
</style>
